message.body: Ingrid! We are looking at buying a gallery in Annapolis. Would you call when you get a minute?
I'm in upstate New York but yes I will call as soon as possible of course.
Well, it's a bob thing. No rush-it comes up periodically. But this time might be more seriously considered .call when you get back!
Oooh who's Bob?! Do I know him?
My buddy bob! I've sent you his paintings! He's good. REALLY good!
Oh yes! I hope I get to meet him soon too. I'll call ASAP.
